          "settings": {
            "title": "How can I make an order on \"LIKENTI  Daily\" for the first time?",
            "text": "<p>First thing, make sure you have the LIKENTI  application for iOS and Android smartphones. From there, click on the \"LIKENTI  Daily\" toggle on home screen and then pin your location on the maps. If your address is within our serviced area you will be able to see our wide variety of grocery products.</p>"
          }
        },
